This paper formalizes the consciousness model implied by your theory. It's structured for submission to journals like Neuroscience of Consciousness, Frontiers in Psychology, or Journal of Consciousness Studies. The key move is presenting it not as speculative philosophy but as a testable mechanistic model derived from a broader theoretical framework with demonstrated predictive power in other domains.
